.TH CYGNUS-MEDIA 0.3 "March 2026" "Version 0.3" "Cygnus Media Player"
.SH NAME
cygnus-media \- lightweight media player for Cygnus WM

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cygnus-media
[\fIFILE\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cygnus-media
is a simple media player built using SDL2 and FFmpeg for the Cygnus Window Manager. It handles both audio and video playback. If no file is provided, it launches a file picker (\fBcygnus-open\fR).

.SH KEY BINDINGS
.TP
.B Space
Pause/Resume playback.
.TP
.B Left Arrow
Rewind 10 seconds.
.TP
.B Right Arrow
Fast forward 10 seconds.
.TP
.B Up Arrow
Volume Up.
.TP
.B Down Arrow
Volume Down.
.TP
.B q, Escape
Exit the player.

